caption: ⚡💜 Liora, the neon-lit cyberpunk queen, dashes through rain-soaked neon alley, her silver crop-top revealing a sculpted chest, she slashes a holographic display as she leaps over a hovering drone, her bold confidence radiating in a futuristic cityscape that glows with electric blue and magenta, capturing the eye of every passerby in a cinematic Instagram post.
